My build of st, the simple terminal by suckless.org based on Luke's build (https://github.com/LukeSmithxyz/st)

# Custom bindings
scrollback with alt-k/j or alt-PgUp/PgDn
alt-shift-PgUp/PgDn to increase/decrease font size, alt-home returns to default
alt-c to copy, alt-v to paste
alt-l to follow urls
alt-y to copy urls
alt-o tp copy the output of commands from stdout

# Patches applied
- xresources
- alpha
- vertcenter
- Scrollback
- font2
- selectioncolors
- hidecursor

# Installation
git clone https://github.com/hybryd0ng/SB
cd SB/st
sudo make install

# Recompilation
sudo make clean install
